    	        arr.append(mat[i][j])
    	        
    	return arr[-1]
-------------------------------------
Complexity Analysis
Time Complexity: O(M*N*(log(M*N))), sorting the linear array takes time complexity of O(M*N(logM*N)).
Space Complexity: O(M*N), to create a linear array.
